{"tid":1942503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港交所：上周五一名出席上市儀式嘉賓確診","createTime":"2020-03-25T06:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T06:26:03.000Z","uid":173598,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db71ebe523186a0314da82974d2c7ed9c09129ee","tid":1942503,"uid":173598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"香港交易所表示，獲悉曾於3月20日到訪香港金融大會堂出席新股上市儀式的一位嘉賓，已被確診感染新型冠狀病毒肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n交易所正在聯繫所有於當日出席活動的人士，並已在金融大會堂進行徹底消毒及清潔，而金融大會堂自當日上市儀式後，再沒有舉辦任何其他活動。<br />\n<br />\n交易所表示，一直以嘉賓及員工的健康和安全為首要考慮，會繼續密切留意事態發展，必要時將重新審視相關安排。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516715-20200325.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516715-20200325.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=5936ce70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516715-20200325.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=183ff119\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516715-20200325.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354de753579fb99315d42ff937b9371925990896","tid":1942503,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}